Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.15,0:23:53.30,Default CN,,0,0,0,,渚 难得来一趟祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.30,0:23:54.22,Default JP,,0,0,0,,楽しみましょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.30,0:23:54.22,Default CN,,0,0,0,,就好好享受呗？
